        title: 'What services does TrinityOps provide?',
        description:
          'TrinityOps helps startups and teams simplify their infrastructure. We build cloud and/or self-hosted, cost-efficient platforms using Kubernetes, Helm, ArgoCD, and observability tools like Grafana, Alloy and Loki, among others. We also mentor aspiring technologists and teach practical DevOps from the ground up.',
