        title: 'Do you only work with self-hosted systems?',
        description:
          "Self-hosting is our specialty — but not a requirement. We help teams avoid unnecessary cloud dependency and design hybrid solutions where it makes sense. If you're using GKE, EKS, or AKS, we can still help you clean up, secure, and simplify your stack.",
      },
      {
        title: 'What are your consulting rates and project costs?',
        description:
          'Our consulting rates start at $199/hour, or via fixed-scope engagements ranging from $5K–$25K depending on the size and urgency of the work. We also offer mentorship and field support at reduced rates through our apprenticeship program.',
